{"tid":2179120,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯下週歸隊訓練 高文將他拒諸門外","createTime":"2020-08-29T01:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T07:36:00.000Z","uid":147522,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"a00bb616678d8a367b0966bb4819f29eeb6119ff","tid":2179120,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:22:48.000Z","msg":"　　儘管已經決定離隊，但美斯（Lionel Messi）仍將在下週一參加巴塞隆拿的訓練，原因是他的法律團隊不想授人以柄。<br />\n<br />\n　　美斯和巴塞未來有可能就合約條款問題走上法庭，為此，美斯方面要儘可能少的給對方以口實，如果拒不參加球隊訓練，將被視為違規違約之舉，如果未來發生法律糾紛，這對美斯是不利的。<br />\n<br />\n　　不過，《TyC Sports》稱，巴塞新帥高文（Ronald Koeman）尚未決定，在風波中，是否接受美斯和一隊球員們一起訓練，因為這可能對球隊氣氛產生不良影響，亦有可能單獨安排美斯練習，最大程度避免麻煩。"},{"pid":"40a4fe6567036bc49f294032c437208c7d09a305","tid":2179120,"uid":23833,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:55:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df76c258cfaf549acf9e3be75a67c2df85bb54ff","tid":2179120,"uid":38271,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:57:27.000Z","msg":"巴塞 皇馬主要的分別其實唔係足球技術<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係人情味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9989fc167d95ba8e6e1f56c98d494f8c263948ba","tid":2179120,"uid":4957,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:58:56.000Z","msg":"高文 做得好！<br />\n支持你清除球霸"},{"pid":"7dba534f6c9397d99614c1ac5d485d5b25926314","tid":2179120,"uid":27946,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T03:01:09.000Z","msg":"高文再過火d隨時準備比人拆埋球場都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6d7f4b6cbca83e9fb4d919a6e0ac382c4e9ab3","tid":2179120,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"高文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f